      <title>美国人现在对其他债务支付的利息与抵押贷款一样多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/americans-now-pay-as-much-interest-on-other-debt-as-on-mortgages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据经济分析局的最新数据，美国家庭现在为从信用卡到学生贷款等其他类型的债务支付的利息与抵押贷款的利息大致相同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/americans-now-pay-as-much-interest-on-other-debt-as-on-mortgages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
