    <item>
      <title>部长表示，SSR 将支付土耳其矿山山体滑坡清理费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/ssr-mining-to-pay-for-landslide-cleanup-at-copler-gold-mine-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府高级官员表示，SSR 矿业公司的土耳其子公司将支付土耳其东部科普勒金矿发生山体滑坡后的所有清理费用，但没有透露具体数字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/ssr-mining-to-pay-for-landslide-cleanup-at-copler-gold-mine-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟提议首期拨款 15 亿欧元以振兴国防部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/eu-proposes-initial-1-5-billion-to-galvanize-defense-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最初拨出 15 亿欧元（合 16 亿美元）来促进欧盟的国防工业，该提议可能会面临担心布鲁塞尔攫取过多权力的国家的抵制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/eu-proposes-initial-1-5-billion-to-galvanize-defense-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LME 表示市场对于绿镍期货来说还不够大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/lme-says-green-nickel-market-not-large-enough-for-own-futures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所表示，所谓的“绿色镍”市场太小，无法保证自己的期货合约，这对希望获得金属溢价的矿商来说是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/lme-says-green-nickel-market-not-large-enough-for-own-futures</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国推出养老金计划，基金目标为 2000 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/germany-unveils-pension-package-with-200-billion-fund-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟公布了确保长期国家养老金融资的计划，包括在未来十年中期建立一个基金，用于投资价值至少 2000 亿欧元（2170 亿美元）的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/germany-unveils-pension-package-with-200-billion-fund-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着采矿业的反弹，南非避免了经济衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/south-african-economy-averts-recession-as-mining-sector-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非经济在第四季度摆脱了技术性衰退，轮流停电次数减少帮助采矿业等能源密集型行业反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/south-african-economy-averts-recession-as-mining-sector-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜耳承诺解决法律问题，利润将下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/bayer-forecasts-another-year-of-falling-profit-keeps-structure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜耳公司预计今年利润将再次下降，并选择暂时坚持其集团结构，因为该公司正在努力克服威胁公司长期未来的数十亿美元的法律困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/bayer-forecasts-another-year-of-falling-profit-keeps-structure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街受到技术下滑和鹰派美联储言论的打击：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储政策制定者的鹰派言论强化了美联储并不急于降息的信息，而三大科技巨头则打压了美国股指期货，股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
